&lt;h2&gt;


🤖 AI-Powered Dynamic Translation
&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Static UI translations are great, but what about user-generated content?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;


The Dynamic Content Challenge
&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Your app probably has:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Event descriptions&lt;/strong&gt; written by organizers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;User bios&lt;/strong&gt; in their preferred language&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Comments and posts&lt;/strong&gt; from the community&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Notifications&lt;/strong&gt; generated by the system&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You can't pre-translate these. You need AI.&lt;/p&gt;

