&lt;h3&gt;


3. Manual Testing Checklist
&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;[ ]  All UI elements translate&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;[ ]  No layout breaks (especially with longer text)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;[ ]  Language switcher works from any page&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;[ ]  Language persists on page reload&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;[ ]  Fallback works if translation missing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;[ ]  Dynamic content translates (if applicable)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;[ ]  Forms validate in correct language&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;[ ]  Error messages display in correct language&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;




